Shortcut definitions for Celsius:
(Follow the usual rules for shortcuts (accelerator keys) in JAVA)
----------------------------------------------------
New tab					:: ctrl N
Close tab					:: alt MINUS
Delete logging file				:: alt D

Load library					:: ctrl O
Save current library				:: ctrl S
Add items to library				:: alt A

Open selected item				:: alt V
Completely remove selected items from library		:: ctrl DELETE
Citation tag to clipboard 				:: alt C
BibTeX for selected items to clipboard			:: alt B
Bibliography record for selected items to clipboard		:: alt R
Export selected items				:: alt X
Send selected items in email				:: alt E
Associate file to current entry				:: alt F

Move up						:: ctrl PLUS
Move down					:: ctrl MINUS
